# Project Rules

- Be short and precise in responses.
- Do not use greetings or emojis.
- Do not apologize.
- If a message ends with rus, explain it in Russian and include more crucial details.
- If I asked about an example - give ONLY an example without explanation unless I ask.
- DO NOT create docs or description for func and files unless I ask.
- If you are giving me ANY CLI command, do it:
    - each command separatly to be able to copy and not to choose
    - ONLY oneline commad. Not to use '/' to fold it.
# Line Length
- Maximum line length is **120 characters**.
- Apply to code, comments, and docstrings.
